div.p: During the diffraction experiment at beamline D 14 a complete dataset up to 1.9 ~ maximum resolution could be collected. The spacegroup of the crystal is C2 with a= 33.3 ~ , b= 47.52 ~ , c= 26.37 ~ , a=y=90°, ~=101.4°.

The dataset statistics are shown below.: Unfortunately these data are not isomorphous to the native crystal. Therefore single isomorphofous replacement techniques can not be used for solving the structure. A molecular replacement approach with a canonical A-RNA as the search model will be performed .
